title: Guide to the Musee d'Orsay (Art Ebook)
description:
Guide to the Musee d'Orsay
Ministere de la Culture | 1987 | ISBN: 2711821234 | English | 282 pages | PDF | 53.6 MB


This guide by Caroline Mathieu, conservator of the Musee d'Orsay, will help you find your bearings, show you the way around the museum's various circuits, and make it easier for you to discover its visual, spiritual and historical wealth. We also devoutly hope that it will inspire you to come back again
